title: Eastpak orbit black
description:
• One main compartment
  • Front pocket
  • Comfortable padded back
  • Thick padded shoulder straps
description_long:
It’s sweet, it’s chic! A most beloved smaller version of the classic Padded Pak'r®, Eastpak Orbit is the ideal solution for day trips andweekend getaways to the countryside. Its ergonomic design, padded back and straps will make the weight feel lighter, while its roomy inner compartment is perfect for keeping your little things safe and sound.
Available in a wide variety of colours and designs.

description:
• Reflective inserts
  • Two large compartments including padded protected sleeve for books
  • Laptop accessible from the in- and outside
  • Multi compartment organizer pocket with detachable pouch
  • Side mesh bottle holder
  • Comfortable raised panels air mesh back
  • S-shape padded shoulder straps with reflective piping and sternum strap
  • Reinforced padded bottom with extra corner protection

description_long:
Protect your laptop and be prepared in style with the Eastpak Egghead backpack. Large compartments with reinforced padding help to keep your laptop safe, while useful pockets and organisers mean everything you need is on hand. Ergonomic padded shoulder straps make the Egghead comfortable to wear – no wonder it’s a best-seller!
The Eastpak Egghead backpack comes in a range of great colours and designs.
